casebody.data:
Deirdre A. CLIFFORD, petitioner,
v.
ROCKLAND COUNTY, NEW YORK. No. 13-7398. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 21, 2014.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until February 11, 2014, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in *1019compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
